> Just another .02 worth. Had a friend with a fairly aggressive cam grind
> and the available vacuum was a little slow coming with all the valve
> overlap. When he had to sit at a red light, the brake peddle would get hard
> and lose assist.
>   We installed a "Vacuum reservoir canister" in line (ala 1950s style
> domestic cars) and cured the problem.
>   Just a thought.
